<i>sub to find some dolphins.</i>

12:53.973 --> 13:01.313
♪

13:01.380 --> 13:02.648
(Dolphins chirping)

13:02.715 --> 13:04.350
Look! Some customers!

13:04.416 --> 13:05.718
{\an3}(Chirping)

13:05.784 --> 13:10.389
♪

13:10.456 --> 13:13.058
{\an3}(Chirping)

13:13.125 --> 13:14.393
You got it, sir!

13:14.460 --> 13:17.396
One single scoop of mint
chocolate fish, please!

13:17.463 --> 13:19.999
A single scoop
means one scoop.

13:21.667 --> 13:24.136
Here you go!
A single scoop.

13:24.203 --> 13:26.205
(Whistling in alarm)

13:26.272 --> 13:28.807
MOLLY:
What happened?

13:28.874 --> 13:31.944
{\an5}(Gasping)

13:28.874 --> 13:31.944
Tiger shark!

13:32.011 --> 13:34.580
Let's get out of here!

13:34.647 --> 13:39.919
♪

13:39.985 --> 13:42.388
MOLLY:
Oh, that was a close one!

13:42.454 --> 13:45.357
{\an5}DEEMA:
Let's find somewhere else
to serve our ice cream.

13:45.424 --> 13:46.825
<i>So they drove their</i>
<i>ice cream sub</i>

13:46.892 --> 13:48.794
<i>to find some other dolphins.</i>

13:48.861 --> 13:50.996
{\an3}(Chirping)

13:53.532 --> 13:56.602
Buongiorno! What can I get
for you today?

13:56.669 --> 13:58.604
(Clicking, chirping)

13:58.671 --> 14:01.273
One double fish ripple,
coming right up!

14:01.340 --> 14:03.542
Double means two!

14:03.609 --> 14:07.112
There's one scoop, and two.

14:07.179 --> 14:08.147
A double!

14:08.214 --> 14:09.381
Here you go!

14:09.448 --> 14:11.483
<i>But once again...</i>

14:11.550 --> 14:13.886
{\an3}(Shrieking)

14:13.953 --> 14:16.188
