listen for the echo.

20:22.287 --> 20:25.023
Then he'll be able to figure
out what's over there.

20:25.090 --> 20:26.658
(Chirping)

20:29.595 --> 20:30.929
We need your help!

20:30.996 --> 20:31.930
Ready, Buddy?

20:31.997 --> 20:33.198
(Chirping)

