That looks like a party hat!

20:39.471 --> 20:41.473
(Clicking,
horn sounding)

20:41.540 --> 20:42.975
(Horn sounding,
sonar beeping)

20:43.041 --> 20:45.444
That looks like a present!

20:45.510 --> 20:46.912
(Clicking,
horn sounding)

20:46.979 --> 20:48.347
(Horn sounding,
sonar beeping)

20:48.413 --> 20:51.283
